reviewText: Lover this! Combined with good nutrition, my husband and I are seeing fantastic results!!
I would purchase from seller again however I have not completed the dvd series.  It is very challenging.
I LOVE Jillian and The Biggest Loser rocks!!! What's not to love about this box set?? It's a win-win situation.
I love these DVD's. Jillian is tough but they are effective.  I would recommend them to anyone wanting results & willing to work for them.
